{#} This template will recap the stp configuration for each device.
And will perform a check of the values to give a compliance result OK or KO
exemple:
Host: R1, stp correctly configured, OK
Host: R2, stp not configured, KO
{#}
# stp Compliance report:
# ------------------------
{% for host,facts in hostvars|dictsort %}
Host: {{host}},{% if not facts.log_result.failed  %} stp configured, OK{% else %} stp not configured correctly, KO{% endif %}

{% endfor %}
